statements.statement: SELECT concat( trim(C.CSM_CAT_DESC), " - ", trim(S.CSM_SUB_CAT_DESC)) FROM CSM_CATEGORIES C, CSM_SUB_CATEGORIES S, CSM_CAT_SUB_XREF R PLAN C WHERE C.CSM_CAT_ID > 0 JOIN S WHERE S.CSM_SUB_CAT_ID > 0 JOIN R WHERE R.CSM_CAT_ID = C.CSM_CAT_ID AND R.CSM_SUB_CAT_ID = S.CSM_SUB_CAT_ID AND R.CSM_CALLBACK_IND = 0 AND R.ACTIVE_IND = 0
select c.csm_prior_desc from csm_priorities c where c.csm_prior_id > 0 and c.csm_active_ind = 1
